Me and my momma who birthed me on this day 49 years ago.  Everything about me that is sweet is her, and the darker parts of me too that I hold that she couldn’t. My eyes, my hands, my cheeks and smile and especially my heart is her. Thank you SandyMomma for giving me the gift of this wonderful and wounded life. Forever lovingly you. Especially on this day of our birth day.

⭐️COLLEGEN BOOSTING LASER TREATMENT ⭐️

This is a non surgical approach to skin care maintenance. I have no fillers and no botox.  Microcurrent and red light therapy have been my mainstay technological treatments until I recently discovered this amazing pain free collegen boosting laser administered lovingly by @sameirodacosta  PS please ignore my nasal voice, recovering from a wicked head cold  The machine specifics are ….Cfu-èlife Biotec Italia 
Much more precise than HiFu

WE WON’T GO BACK! One year ago today, Roe v. Wade was overturned by the Supreme Court against the will of the majority of the American people, immediately impacting everyone with and without reproductive organs by rescinding the almost fifty-year-old national right to an abortion. A year may have passed, but the fight is far from over, and @feminist and @doubledutchcash have teamed up to help you make an impact! Continue to defend your rights in full force with beauty and generosity by sending this powerful image by our founders @inezandvinoodh of the gorgeously fierce @shalomharlow and @raquel_zimmermann —along with a donation to @sistersong_woc , @reprorights , or @abortionfunds in our “Equity & Access” charity drop-down at checkout —to a friend, loved one, or elected official today, and let them know the fight continues. Xx DD

Visit the #linkinbio to send a card via @doubledutchcash or to Protect Abortion Access for all with @feminist ‘s toolkit.

Today is also the Nationwide Day of Action and Solidarity! Visit @womensmarch to find a gathering in the city near you!

#abortionisahumanright #abortionishealthcare #abortionisawomansright #art #artistsoninstagram #artwork #artist #generosity #giving #charity #doubledutch #feminist #roevwade #dobbsvjackson #womensmarch #womensmarch2023
